    "collapsible_tabs_KNKLiF": {
      "type": "collapsible-tabs",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_item_t7UtgE": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Does Proferlo have a showroom I can visit?",
            "content": "<p>No — Proferlo is online-only with no physical showroom. Our Acacia Ridge, Brisbane location is a warehouse and dispatch centre only and isn't open to the public. Selling factory-direct online is how we keep quality high without the retail markup. Every product page has detailed photos, exact dimensions, and real customer reviews so you can buy with confidence.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": true
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_AMx7Wd": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "What if I change my mind?",
            "content": "<p>We offer 14-day change-of-mind returns. If a piece doesn't feel right in your space, you can return it within 14 days of delivery — you just cover the return shipping. Items need to be unused and in their original packaging.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_rUAHxc": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "How long does delivery take?",
            "content": "<p>Delivery takes 2–4 business days to metro areas, with regional areas taking a little longer. We ship Australia-wide via our  express couriers from our Brisbane warehouse, and you'll receive tracking as soon as your order is dispatched.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_JCwmkt": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Why are Proferlo's prices lower than furniture retailers?",
            "content": "<p>Proferlo is factory-direct — we own the factory that makes our furniture, so there's no middleman markup. You're paying for the materials and craftsmanship, not a chain of wholesalers and showroom overheads. Smart choice, same quality.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_afrmKt": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Is Proferlo furniture sustainably made?",
            "content": "<p>Yes — our timber is FSC-certified and our boards meet CARB Phase 2 low-emission standards. Our factory is also certified to ISO 9001, ISO 14001, and ISO 45001, and audited under BSCI. Quality that holds up, made responsibly.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_HynDyF": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Will my furniture need assembly?",
            "content": "<p>Most Proferlo furniture requires some flat-pack assembly, and each product page states exactly what's involved. Our pieces are designed for straightforward setup — clear instructions, labelled parts, no engineering degree required.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_HURCdi": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Can I buy now and pay later?",
            "content": "<p>Yes — we accept Afterpay, Zip Pay, and PayPal Pay Later, plus all major cards and PayPal. Split your purchase into interest-free instalments and style your space now.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        }
      },
